{
  "id": "5aef946860d3e10014f3a6be",
  "title": "書籍は何を売っていたのか",
  "created": 1525650540,
  "updated": 1525653031,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5aef946860d3e10014f3a6be",
      "text": "書籍は何を売っていたのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650540,
      "updated": 1525652095
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef946caff09e00008e3917",
      "text": " 作成過程の自分観察がこちらにある: [20180502自分観察ログ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650540,
      "updated": 1525651448
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef97f9aff09e00008e392a",
      "text": "\t「マッハ新書以前の書籍は何を売っていたのか」という問いを見てもう一歩進んだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651449,
      "updated": 1525651527
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9478aff09e0000625181",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650553,
      "updated": 1525650553
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9479aff09e0000625183",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/accbe15f3fd41f9f4fad905941a028cd]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650554,
      "updated": 1525650554
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b3aaff09e00008e393e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652283,
      "updated": 1525652283
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b3baff09e00008e393f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652283,
      "updated": 1525652283
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9482aff09e0000625184",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650562,
      "updated": 1525650562
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b3daff09e00008e3944",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/17cbb52f6547410bf2979621c64d34ae]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652286,
      "updated": 1525652286
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef946caff09e00008e3918",
      "text": " AさんとBさんが近くにいて、教えるAさんの行動をBさんが観察できる状況",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650541,
      "updated": 1525650598
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9547aff09e00008e3919",
      "text": "  まずAさんの作業をBさんが傍で見ることによって非言語的な伝達が行われる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650759,
      "updated": 1525650840
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9597aff09e00008e391d",
      "text": "  経験の共通化 #共同化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650840,
      "updated": 1525650843
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9581aff09e00008e391c",
      "text": "  共通の経験をAさんがどう解釈しているか言葉で伝えることによって、解釈の共通化が行われる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650818,
      "updated": 1525650868
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef959daff09e00008e391e",
      "text": "   そのままほっておくとBさんがBさんなりの解釈をする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650846,
      "updated": 1525650846
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b40aff09e00008e3945",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652289,
      "updated": 1525652289
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b40aff09e00008e3946",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652289,
      "updated": 1525652289
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9479aff09e0000625182",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650554,
      "updated": 1525650554
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b46aff09e00008e3952",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0e9660b06eb6eb51ed57e14a6971127d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652294,
      "updated": 1525652294
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9540aff09e0000625185",
      "text": "\t教える人と教わる人が離れていて直接観察できない場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650756,
      "updated": 1525650897
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef95d1aff09e00008e3921",
      "text": " \t書籍などでよくある状況",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650897,
      "updated": 1525650902
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef95d6aff09e00008e3922",
      "text": " まずAさんが言語化をする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650902,
      "updated": 1525650981
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9625aff09e00008e3923",
      "text": "  しかしこの時に、言語化が難しい経験は取りこぼされる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650981,
      "updated": 1525650999
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef964daff09e00008e3924",
      "text": "  生の経験を書籍の形で運ぶことができない場合がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651021,
      "updated": 1525651048
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9668aff09e00008e3925",
      "text": "  経験を解釈し言語化したものになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651048,
      "updated": 1525651055
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9ae4aff09e00008e393a",
      "text": " 共同観察できる状態よりは劣った学びのフォーマットである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652196,
      "updated": 1525652211
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9aeeaff09e00008e393b",
      "text": " \tが、スケールする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652207,
      "updated": 1525652214
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9afeaff09e00008e393c",
      "text": "  教育をする側の増加よりも速く教育を受ける側が増えた状況下で有効",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652222,
      "updated": 1525652266
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b50aff09e00008e3953",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652305,
      "updated": 1525652305
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b25aff09e00008e393d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652262,
      "updated": 1525652298
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b53aff09e00008e3955",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9040023c449174607fab46bc770b5f69]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652307,
      "updated": 1525652307
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef96a7aff09e0000625189",
      "text": " 抽象化され言語化された本を読んだBさんは、その言語化された解釈を、自分の経験と結びつける必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651113,
      "updated": 1525652317
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef95cbaff09e00008e3920",
      "text": "\t\t腹に落ちる、血肉になる、などのメタファー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650891,
      "updated": 1525651304
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef98c6aff09e000062518c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651660,
      "updated": 1525651668
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9618aff09e0000625187",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525650970,
      "updated": 1525650970
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b63aff09e00008e3958",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9a53d18ca7247795234ba5e16c1f090f]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652323,
      "updated": 1525652323
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef96acaff09e000062518a",
      "text": "\tこの「自分の経験との結合」は容易なものではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651117,
      "updated": 1525651344
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9790aff09e00008e3928",
      "text": " そこで著者側は、かみ砕いた説明をしたり、具体例を入れたり、小説形式にしたり、「漫画でわかる」形式にしたりする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651344,
      "updated": 1525651407
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef97c5aff09e00008e3929",
      "text": " これは著者側がコストを掛けることによって読者に歩み寄っている構造",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651397,
      "updated": 1525651576
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef98e9aff09e00008e392e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651689,
      "updated": 1525651689
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef98e7aff09e00008e392d",
      "text": " 少品種[大量生産]の時代にはそれでもよかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651687,
      "updated": 1525651710
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef98d6aff09e00008e392c",
      "text": "\t\t大勢の読者によって著者のコストを負担するから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651670,
      "updated": 1525651778
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef99c9aff09e00008e3933",
      "text": "  著者がコストをかけて「わかりやすい本」を書くと長く多く売れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651913,
      "updated": 1525651984
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9a10aff09e00008e3934",
      "text": "  コストを掛けることが正当化された",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651984,
      "updated": 1525651988
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9942aff09e00008e3930",
      "text": " 分野の細分化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651778,
      "updated": 1525651866
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef999aaff09e00008e3932",
      "text": " 市場に出てくる商品の種類の増加",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651866,
      "updated": 1525651866
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef998daff09e00008e3931",
      "text": " 1冊の本あたりの読者の量が減少した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651853,
      "updated": 1525651867
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9a2eaff09e00008e3936",
      "text": " 書籍の[シグナリング]の効果の減少",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652014,
      "updated": 1525652032
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef991aaff09e00008e392f",
      "text": "  [悪貨は良貨を駆逐する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525651739,
      "updated": 1525652057
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9a28aff09e00008e3935",
      "text": " インターネットの登場",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652008,
      "updated": 1525652104
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9a88aff09e00008e3938",
      "text": " \tインターネット上での情報流通の質・量・速度に比較して、書籍という流通経路の魅力が減少",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652104,
      "updated": 1525652126
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b6faff09e00008e3959",
      "text": " 著者側のそれをやるインセンティブが薄れている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652335,
      "updated": 1525652345
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9e20aff09e00008e396b",
      "text": " 読者側も情報洪水に溺れている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525653024,
      "updated": 1525653031
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9bf9aff09e00008e3960",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652473,
      "updated": 1525652473
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9bf9aff09e00008e3961",
      "text": "\tアジャイルとウォーターフォール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652473,
      "updated": 1525652483
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9c02aff09e00008e3962",
      "text": " \t書籍は、顧客(読者)が目の前にいない状態で書きあげる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652483,
      "updated": 1525652509
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9c1daff09e00008e3963",
      "text": "  これは大変",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652509,
      "updated": 1525652514
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9c22aff09e00008e3964",
      "text": "  コストをかけて作成した後で、顧客が存在しないことに気付くと問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652514,
      "updated": 1525652533
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9c35aff09e00008e3965",
      "text": "  \t関連: [リーン・スタートアップ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652533,
      "updated": 1525652541
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9c4caff09e00008e3966",
      "text": "\t\t著者の側としては顧客の反応をなるべく早く知りたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652557,
      "updated": 1525652567
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9c57aff09e00008e3967",
      "text": "  \tレビュワーの導入など",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652567,
      "updated": 1525652579
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9cfbaff09e00008e3968",
      "text": "  ソフトウェア業界では一足早く類似の考え方に到った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652731,
      "updated": 1525652752
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9d0faff09e00008e3969",
      "text": "  \tリリース可能なものをなるべく早く作ってリリースする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652752,
      "updated": 1525652768
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9d1faff09e00008e396a",
      "text": "   顧客との対話を通じて作るべきものが何かを明らかにする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652768,
      "updated": 1525652776
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9ba6aff09e00008e395b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652390,
      "updated": 1525652554
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9b74aff09e00008e395a",
      "text": "整理",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652340,
      "updated": 1525652394
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9ba9aff09e00008e395d",
      "text": "\t書籍は何を売っていたか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652394,
      "updated": 1525652399
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9baeaff09e00008e395e",
      "text": "  抽象化された概念と、抽象化された概念を読者が自分の経験と結合することの支援",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652399,
      "updated": 1525652475
    },
    {
      "id": "5aef9bd2aff09e00008e395f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525652434,
      "updated": 1525652471
    }
  ]
}